OL,6,FNurses are set to take strike action
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland by November if a
OL,8,F#200 million funding gap is not
OL,9,Fbridged to meet a recommended pay
OL,10,Fincrease, the Health Minister has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FMike Nesbitt told MLAs that the impact
OL,14,Fof strike action on efforts to drive
OL,15,Fdown the region's waiting lists would
OL,16,Fbe "massive".
OL,18,FThe minister said his department was
OL,19,Ffacing a #614 million funding gap. He
OL,20,Fsaid #200 million of that sum related
OL,21,Fto nurses' pay.
