OL,6,FThe minister was responding to a
OL,7,Fquestion from SDLP MLA Colin McGrath
OL,8,Fwho accused the Executive of being
OL,9,Funwilling to pay health workers "what
OL,10,Fthey are owed".
OL,12,FIn response, the minister said he
OL,13,Fwould not point fingers at Executive
OL,14,Fcolleagues over the funding shortfall.
OL,16,F"I don't see a fix for this outside of
OL,17,Fthe Executive working together
OL,18,Fcollaboratively," he said.
