OL,6,F"So, I'm not in the business of
OL,7,Fpointing a finger at any other
OL,8,FExecutive minister.
OL,10,F"I have made the point repeatedly that
OL,11,FI understand every minister, every
OL,12,Fdepartment, is suffering huge
OL,13,Ffinancial pressures. I believe the
OL,14,Fpressures on health are absolutely
OL,15,Funprecedented and we're talking around
OL,16,F#614 million of a funding gap. That's
OL,17,Funprecedented, and there is a question
OL,18,Fabout whether it's unmanageable, and
OL,19,F#200 million of that is for nurses'
OL,20,Fpay.
