OL,6,F"And what I would say to the member
OL,7,Fis, after the last Executive meeting,
OL,8,FI happened to have a meeting with the
OL,9,FRoyal College of Nursing and Nicola
OL,10,FRanger, the chief executive, (having)
OL,11,Fflown in from London, and she made it
OL,12,Fvery clear that they had had enough.
OL,14,F"She also made clear that last time
OL,15,Fthey went on strike, they felt they
OL,16,Fwere too soft, and that their message
OL,17,Fdid not land properly.
